{
  "stem": "2533.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And I couldn't-- I didn't have anything to show.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "But on that same train where I-- not a train, but in the- the same carriage, there was a lady from Chelm with two small children.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And I offered my help.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And she said, all she would like me to do is take the two girls down the carriage and stand on a corner where she will put all the-- her luggage there, the few parcels she had, and hold the children by the hand so they won't go away.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And she went over to the guard to show her papers.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And when everything was all right, she nod her head to me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And I just kicked-- there was a little gate-- kicked the little gate open, and I walked through with the two girls.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] That was the second miracle.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "There were other miracles before, but that's not so important.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But maybe the Germans saw that I am with her because I was holding her children and all that.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Anyhow, I went through.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I knew where the street-- where the employment office was.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I make my way to-- to the [POLISH].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That was one of the posh streets in Lublin.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I saw, you know, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I walked in, because I was going then as a volunteer worker to Germany, because that birth certificate I have was born in Lutsk.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the Ukraines were murdering the Poles there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That was the eastern part of Poland.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I just thought of things, if I am from Lutsk and I was aware that they're working, I couldn't go back because I wasn't actually from the city.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I was outside.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I've heard that something is happening there.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
